:cp_splitter_inlet rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                            elementary:InletConnectionPoint ;
                   elementary:dealsWithStuff Brick:Air ;
                   elementary:isRelatedToVariable :var_air_inlet_flow_rate .


###  http://www.w3id.org/elmentary/applications/hvac#cp_splitter_outlet_a
:cp_splitter_outlet_a rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
                               elementary:OutletConnectionPoint ;
                      elementary:dealsWithStuff Brick:Air ;
